{"template":"__react_static_root__/src/components/QiitaPost","sharedHashesByProp":{},"data":{"post":{"rendered_body":"<p data-sourcepos=\"2:1-2:6\">供養</p>\n<h2 data-sourcepos=\"4:1-4:9\">\n<span id=\"内容\" class=\"fragment\"></span><a href=\"#%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9\"><i class=\"fa fa-link\"></i></a>内容</h2>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"6:1-6:163\"><a href=\"https://camo.qiitausercontent.com/5bf319856fbc6a3d07afd06607c426e1d47297b1/68747470733a2f2f71696974612d696d6167652d73746f72652e73332e61702d6e6f727468656173742d312e616d617a6f6e6177732e636f6d2f302f3131323932392f31346138353536652d333865342d623832642d396133312d6535616337633664376637612e706e67\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://qiita-user-contents.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fqiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F0%2F112929%2F14a8556e-38e4-b82d-9a31-e5ac7c6d7f7a.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.0&amp;auto=format&amp;gif-q=60&amp;q=75&amp;s=67e11cf047c0aae7b647d0b845535338\" alt=\"スクリーンショット 2024-01-10 23.19.42.png\" data-canonical-src=\"https://qiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/0/112929/14a8556e-38e4-b82d-9a31-e5ac7c6d7f7a.png\" srcset=\"https://qiita-user-contents.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fqiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F0%2F112929%2F14a8556e-38e4-b82d-9a31-e5ac7c6d7f7a.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.0&amp;auto=format&amp;gif-q=60&amp;q=75&amp;w=1400&amp;fit=max&amp;s=8feea9841034aade5e8424a8bcb1e10e 1x\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"8:1-8:134\"><a href=\"https://camo.qiitausercontent.com/b6689799aa261d685b1bb48594c67528cb4d1a47/68747470733a2f2f71696974612d696d6167652d73746f72652e73332e61702d6e6f727468656173742d312e616d617a6f6e6177732e636f6d2f302f3131323932392f62333861396332612d663835322d613234342d326136612d3933626636643334373135322e676966\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://qiita-user-contents.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fqiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F0%2F112929%2Fb38a9c2a-f852-a244-2a6a-93bf6d347152.gif?ixlib=rb-4.0.0&amp;auto=format&amp;gif-q=60&amp;q=75&amp;s=77d3547f21b2e84f9c1ff221e92e3a5c\" alt=\"ezgif-1-8078f54032.gif\" data-canonical-src=\"https://qiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/0/112929/b38a9c2a-f852-a244-2a6a-93bf6d347152.gif\" srcset=\"https://qiita-user-contents.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fqiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F0%2F112929%2Fb38a9c2a-f852-a244-2a6a-93bf6d347152.gif?ixlib=rb-4.0.0&amp;auto=format&amp;gif-q=60&amp;q=75&amp;w=1400&amp;fit=max&amp;s=5cbb535c20cbe82ddd3ac21034584ca8 1x\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"10:1-10:21\">で、VSCodeが開く</p>\n<h2 data-sourcepos=\"12:1-12:21\">\n<span id=\"ソースコード\" class=\"fragment\"></span><a href=\"#%E3%82%BD%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B9%E3%82%B3%E3%83%BC%E3%83%89\"><i class=\"fa fa-link\"></i></a>ソースコード</h2>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"14:1-15:66\">fzfは普段から入っているので必要な方はインストールしてください。<br>\nインターラクティブに選択できる部分がそれです</p>\n<div class=\"code-frame\" data-lang=\"bash\" data-sourcepos=\"17:1-21:3\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code><span class=\"nv\">$ </span>brew <span class=\"nb\">install </span>fzf\n<span class=\"nv\">$ </span>vim ~/Documents/bin/OpenQiita\n<span class=\"nv\">$ </span><span class=\"nb\">chmod </span>a+x ~/Documents/bin/OpenQiita\n</code></pre></div></div>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"23:1-23:12\">fzfある版</p>\n<div class=\"code-frame\" data-lang=\"bash\" data-sourcepos=\"25:1-29:3\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code><span class=\"c\">#!/usr/bin/env bash</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">cd</span> ~/workspace/qiita\n<span class=\"nb\">ls</span> <span class=\"nt\">-1</span> | fzf | xargs code\n</code></pre></div></div>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"31:1-32:63\">ない版。<br>\nworkspace/qiitaをvscodeで開く決め打ちになります。</p>\n<div class=\"code-frame\" data-lang=\"text\" data-sourcepos=\"34:1-37:3\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code>#!/usr/bin/env bash\ncode ~/workspace/qiita\n</code></pre></div></div>\n<h2 data-sourcepos=\"39:1-39:22\">\n<span id=\"code動かない方\" class=\"fragment\"></span><a href=\"#code%E5%8B%95%E3%81%8B%E3%81%AA%E3%81%84%E6%96%B9\"><i class=\"fa fa-link\"></i></a>code動かない方</h2>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"42:1-42:163\"><a href=\"https://camo.qiitausercontent.com/93680e168555fa935bc51053ca18b653a07cfa31/68747470733a2f2f71696974612d696d6167652d73746f72652e73332e61702d6e6f727468656173742d312e616d617a6f6e6177732e636f6d2f302f3131323932392f63633737383266382d663231342d373066362d343437632d6133363765376663346338372e706e67\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://qiita-user-contents.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fqiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F0%2F112929%2Fcc7782f8-f214-70f6-447c-a367e7fc4c87.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.0&amp;auto=format&amp;gif-q=60&amp;q=75&amp;s=0d4af87df6871ebec5c2e1d28242b4ee\" alt=\"スクリーンショット 2024-01-10 23.25.14.png\" data-canonical-src=\"https://qiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/0/112929/cc7782f8-f214-70f6-447c-a367e7fc4c87.png\" srcset=\"https://qiita-user-contents.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fqiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F0%2F112929%2Fcc7782f8-f214-70f6-447c-a367e7fc4c87.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.0&amp;auto=format&amp;gif-q=60&amp;q=75&amp;w=1400&amp;fit=max&amp;s=573d3440edd15401fc859cf95fb379df 1x\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"44:1-44:93\">以下のようなコマンドが/usr/local/bin/にインストールされるはずです。</p>\n<div class=\"code-frame\" data-lang=\"shell\" data-sourcepos=\"46:1-50:3\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code><span class=\"nv\">$ </span>which code\n/usr/local/bin/code\n<span class=\"nv\">$ </span>code /usr/local/bin/code\n</code></pre></div></div>\n<div class=\"code-frame\" data-lang=\"bash\" data-sourcepos=\"52:1-89:3\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code><span class=\"c\">#!/usr/bin/env bash</span>\n<span class=\"c\">#</span>\n<span class=\"c\"># Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation. All rights reserved.</span>\n<span class=\"c\"># Licensed under the MIT License. See License.txt in the project root for license information.</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># when run in remote terminal, use the remote cli</span>\n<span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span> <span class=\"nt\">-n</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$VSCODE_IPC_HOOK_CLI</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span> <span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"k\">then\n\t</span><span class=\"nv\">REMOTE_CLI</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"si\">$(</span>which <span class=\"nt\">-a</span> <span class=\"s1\">'code'</span> | <span class=\"nb\">grep</span> /remote-cli/<span class=\"si\">)</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span>\n\t<span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span> <span class=\"nt\">-n</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$REMOTE_CLI</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span> <span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"k\">then</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$REMOTE_CLI</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$@</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"nb\">exit</span> <span class=\"nv\">$?</span>\n\t<span class=\"k\">fi\nfi\n\nfunction </span>app_realpath<span class=\"o\">()</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"nv\">SOURCE</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"nv\">$1</span>\n\t<span class=\"k\">while</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span> <span class=\"nt\">-h</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$SOURCE</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span> <span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"k\">do\n\t\t</span><span class=\"nv\">DIR</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"si\">$(</span><span class=\"nb\">dirname</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$SOURCE</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"si\">)</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"nv\">SOURCE</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"si\">$(</span><span class=\"nb\">readlink</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$SOURCE</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"si\">)</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"o\">[[</span> <span class=\"nv\">$SOURCE</span> <span class=\"o\">!=</span> /<span class=\"k\">*</span> <span class=\"o\">]]</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"nv\">SOURCE</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"nv\">$DIR</span>/<span class=\"nv\">$SOURCE</span>\n\t<span class=\"k\">done\n\t</span><span class=\"nv\">SOURCE_DIR</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"si\">$(</span> <span class=\"nb\">cd</span> <span class=\"nt\">-P</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"si\">$(</span> <span class=\"nb\">dirname</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$SOURCE</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span> <span class=\"si\">)</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span> <span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>/dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1 <span class=\"o\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"nb\">pwd</span> <span class=\"si\">)</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span>\n\t<span class=\"nb\">echo</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"k\">${</span><span class=\"nv\">SOURCE_DIR</span><span class=\"p\">%%</span><span class=\"k\">${</span><span class=\"nv\">SOURCE_DIR</span><span class=\"p\">#*.app</span><span class=\"k\">}}</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"nv\">APP_PATH</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"si\">$(</span>app_realpath <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"k\">${</span><span class=\"nv\">BASH_SOURCE</span><span class=\"p\">[0]</span><span class=\"k\">}</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"si\">)</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span>\n<span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span> <span class=\"nt\">-z</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$APP_PATH</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span> <span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"k\">then\n\t</span><span class=\"nb\">echo</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"Unable to determine app path from symlink : </span><span class=\"k\">${</span><span class=\"nv\">BASH_SOURCE</span><span class=\"p\">[0]</span><span class=\"k\">}</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span>\n\t<span class=\"nb\">exit </span>1\n<span class=\"k\">fi\n</span><span class=\"nv\">CONTENTS</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$APP_PATH</span><span class=\"s2\">/Contents\"</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">ELECTRON</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$CONTENTS</span><span class=\"s2\">/MacOS/Electron\"</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">CLI</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$CONTENTS</span><span class=\"s2\">/Resources/app/out/cli.js\"</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">ELECTRON_RUN_AS_NODE</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>1 <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$ELECTRON</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$CLI</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span> <span class=\"nt\">--ms-enable-electron-run-as-node</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"nv\">$@</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">exit</span> <span class=\"nv\">$?</span>\n\n</code></pre></div></div>\n<h2 data-sourcepos=\"91:1-91:45\">\n<span id=\"純正ターミナルを自動で閉じる\" class=\"fragment\"></span><a href=\"#%E7%B4%94%E6%AD%A3%E3%82%BF%E3%83%BC%E3%83%9F%E3%83%8A%E3%83%AB%E3%82%92%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E3%81%A7%E9%96%89%E3%81%98%E3%82%8B\"><i class=\"fa fa-link\"></i></a>純正ターミナルを自動で閉じる</h2>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"93:1-93:163\"><a href=\"https://camo.qiitausercontent.com/5a164519d58d29b18d9f42345dac2d8e931953ed/68747470733a2f2f71696974612d696d6167652d73746f72652e73332e61702d6e6f727468656173742d312e616d617a6f6e6177732e636f6d2f302f3131323932392f30383666626430372d303534372d653737632d363462352d3831646336383035666330652e706e67\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://qiita-user-contents.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fqiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F0%2F112929%2F086fbd07-0547-e77c-64b5-81dc6805fc0e.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.0&amp;auto=format&amp;gif-q=60&amp;q=75&amp;s=484438889b9adc27f6846bd96e101f1f\" alt=\"スクリーンショット 2024-01-10 23.29.47.png\" data-canonical-src=\"https://qiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/0/112929/086fbd07-0547-e77c-64b5-81dc6805fc0e.png\" srcset=\"https://qiita-user-contents.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fqiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F0%2F112929%2F086fbd07-0547-e77c-64b5-81dc6805fc0e.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.0&amp;auto=format&amp;gif-q=60&amp;q=75&amp;w=1400&amp;fit=max&amp;s=421e04441fbbeae8bbbc01019e23ec0e 1x\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n<blockquote data-sourcepos=\"95:1-95:53\">\n<p data-sourcepos=\"95:3-95:53\">シェルが正常に終了した場合は閉じる</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 data-sourcepos=\"98:1-98:9\">\n<span id=\"参考\" class=\"fragment\"></span><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83\"><i class=\"fa fa-link\"></i></a>参考</h2>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"100:1-100:56\"><iframe id=\"qiita-embed-content__303d5bdf54a87d2dfc6b77e47d1acfec\" src=\"https://qiita.com/embed-contents/link-card#qiita-embed-content__303d5bdf54a87d2dfc6b77e47d1acfec\" data-content=\"https%3A%2F%2Ftakuya-1st.hatenablog.jp%2Fentry%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F212723\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;\" height=\"29\">\n</iframe>\n</p>\n<p data-sourcepos=\"102:1-102:51\"><iframe id=\"qiita-embed-content__2beadb481c7cb1e515ee5fdcc014cda7\" src=\"https://qiita.com/embed-contents/link-card#qiita-embed-content__2beadb481c7cb1e515ee5fdcc014cda7\" data-content=\"https%3A%2F%2Fblog.siwa32.com%2Fmac_terminal_exit_to_close%2F\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;\" height=\"29\">\n</iframe>\n</p>\n","body":"\n供養\n\n## 内容\n\n![スクリーンショット 2024-01-10 23.19.42.png](https://qiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/0/112929/14a8556e-38e4-b82d-9a31-e5ac7c6d7f7a.png)\n\n![ezgif-1-8078f54032.gif](https://qiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/0/112929/b38a9c2a-f852-a244-2a6a-93bf6d347152.gif)\n\nで、VSCodeが開く\n\n## ソースコード\n\nfzfは普段から入っているので必要な方はインストールしてください。\nインターラクティブに選択できる部分がそれです\n\n```bash\n$ brew install fzf\n$ vim ~/Documents/bin/OpenQiita\n$ chmod a+x ~/Documents/bin/OpenQiita\n```\n\nfzfある版\n\n```bash\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\ncd ~/workspace/qiita\nls -1 | fzf | xargs code\n```\n\nない版。\nworkspace/qiitaをvscodeで開く決め打ちになります。\n\n```\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\ncode ~/workspace/qiita\n```\n\n## code動かない方\n\n\n![スクリーンショット 2024-01-10 23.25.14.png](https://qiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/0/112929/cc7782f8-f214-70f6-447c-a367e7fc4c87.png)\n\n以下のようなコマンドが/usr/local/bin/にインストールされるはずです。\n\n```shell\n$ which code\n/usr/local/bin/code\n$ code /usr/local/bin/code\n```\n\n```bash\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\n#\n# Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation. All rights reserved.\n# Licensed under the MIT License. See License.txt in the project root for license information.\n\n# when run in remote terminal, use the remote cli\nif [ -n \"$VSCODE_IPC_HOOK_CLI\" ]; then\n\tREMOTE_CLI=\"$(which -a 'code' | grep /remote-cli/)\"\n\tif [ -n \"$REMOTE_CLI\" ]; then\n\t\t\"$REMOTE_CLI\" \"$@\"\n\t\texit $?\n\tfi\nfi\n\nfunction app_realpath() {\n\tSOURCE=$1\n\twhile [ -h \"$SOURCE\" ]; do\n\t\tDIR=$(dirname \"$SOURCE\")\n\t\tSOURCE=$(readlink \"$SOURCE\")\n\t\t[[ $SOURCE != /* ]] && SOURCE=$DIR/$SOURCE\n\tdone\n\tSOURCE_DIR=\"$( cd -P \"$( dirname \"$SOURCE\" )\" >/dev/null 2>&1 && pwd )\"\n\techo \"${SOURCE_DIR%%${SOURCE_DIR#*.app}}\"\n}\n\nAPP_PATH=\"$(app_realpath \"${BASH_SOURCE[0]}\")\"\nif [ -z \"$APP_PATH\" ]; then\n\techo \"Unable to determine app path from symlink : ${BASH_SOURCE[0]}\"\n\texit 1\nfi\nCONTENTS=\"$APP_PATH/Contents\"\nELECTRON=\"$CONTENTS/MacOS/Electron\"\nCLI=\"$CONTENTS/Resources/app/out/cli.js\"\nELECTRON_RUN_AS_NODE=1 \"$ELECTRON\" \"$CLI\" --ms-enable-electron-run-as-node \"$@\"\nexit $?\n\n```\n\n## 純正ターミナルを自動で閉じる\n\n![スクリーンショット 2024-01-10 23.29.47.png](https://qiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/0/112929/086fbd07-0547-e77c-64b5-81dc6805fc0e.png)\n\n> シェルが正常に終了した場合は閉じる\n\n\n## 参考\n\nhttps://takuya-1st.hatenablog.jp/entry/2017/12/09/212723\n\nhttps://blog.siwa32.com/mac_terminal_exit_to_close/\n","coediting":false,"comments_count":0,"created_at":"2024-01-10T23:27:01+09:00","group":null,"id":"42420b478a4f83278c5f","likes_count":0,"private":false,"reactions_count":0,"stocks_count":0,"tags":[{"name":"ShellScript","versions":[]},{"name":"Terminal","versions":[]},{"name":"VSCode","versions":[]}],"title":"毎日VSCodeで開くプロジェクトをSpotlightに登録して爆速開封の儀","updated_at":"2024-01-10T23:30:12+09:00","url":"https://qiita.com/ykhirao/items/42420b478a4f83278c5f","user":{"description":"Web Developer From 2016.\r\nPHP/Laravel && React/TypeScript/Node.js\r\n\r\n業務委託の依頼とかはWantedlyとかからでお願いします！","facebook_id":"","followees_count":39,"followers_count":100,"github_login_name":"ykhirao","id":"ykhirao","items_count":83,"linkedin_id":"","location":"Tokyo, Japan","name":"yk","organization":"","permanent_id":112929,"profile_image_url":"https://qiita-image-store.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/0/112929/profile-images/1639030792","team_only":false,"twitter_screen_name":"ykhirao","website_url":"https://www.wantedly.com/id/ykhirao"},"page_views_count":null,"team_membership":null,"organization_url_name":null,"slide":false}},"path":"posts/42420b478a4f83278c5f"}
